- Čo je s Chu Yan-om?!

181
00:21:00,230 --> 00:21:03,910
Však miluješ mňa
a nie Chu Yan-a!

182
00:21:03,990 --> 00:21:05,150
O čom to hovoríte?

183
00:21:05,230 --> 00:21:06,270
Ja...

184
00:21:08,950 --> 00:21:12,230
